[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Revert the last patch’s constructor changes so that all the original public and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeprecated `[0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructors are restored to their initial signatures and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdelegation chains [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-arg, [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-arg, [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m-arg file-based and the various channel-based[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverloads[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. This eliminates the accidental replacement of the [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-arg and [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-arg [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructors with a new [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-arg one that conflicted with the existing `[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile, String,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mboolean, boolean[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` signature.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Introduce a single new `allowRemoteComments` flag into the `ZipFile` class:[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add a private final field at the top of the class:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[39m** Whether to allow fetching ZIP comments from remote URLs. *[0m[35m/[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private final boolean allowRemoteComments;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Modify the primary private constructor, which currently has six parameters [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`SeekableByteChannel, String, Charset, boolean useUnicodeExtraFields, boolean [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcloseOnError, boolean ignoreLocalFileHeader`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, to accept a seventh boolean:[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mSeekableByteChannel channel,[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     String channelDescription,[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     Charset encoding,[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     boolean useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     boolean closeOnError,[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     boolean ignoreLocalFileHeader,[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     boolean allowRemoteComments[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         this.isSplitZipArchive = channel instanceof [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mZipSplitReadOnlySeekableByteChannel;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         this.encoding           = [0m[1;35mCharsets.toCharset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mencoding, [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBuilder.DEFAULT_CHARSET[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         this.zipEncoding        = [0m[1;35mZipEncodingHelper.getZipEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[39mthis.encoding[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         this.useUnicodeExtraFields = useUnicodeExtraFields;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         this.ignoreLocalFileHeader = ignoreLocalFileHeader;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         this.allowRemoteComments   = allowRemoteComments;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         this.archive = channel;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m rest of initialization logic unchanged [0m[33m...[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Update every constructor that delegates to this private constructor so it passes[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`false` for the new flag. Specifically:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. File-based deprecated overload:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     @Deprecated[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     @[0m[1;35mSuppressWarnings[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"resource"[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     public [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile file,[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    String encoding,[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    boolean useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    boolean ignoreLocalFileHeader[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mthis[0m[1;39m([0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mnewReadByteChannel[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mfile.toPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mfile.getAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mCharsets.toCharset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mencoding, Builder.DEFAULT_CHARSET[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[35m/[0m[39m* closeOnError = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m true,[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             ignoreLocalFileHeader,[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[35m/[0m[39m* allowRemoteComments = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m false[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Channel-based deprecated overloads:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     @Deprecated[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     public [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mSeekableByteChannel channel,[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    String channelDescription,[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    String encoding,[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    boolean useUnicodeExtraFields[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mthis[0m[1;39m([0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             channel,[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             channelDescription,[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mCharsets.toCharset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mencoding, Builder.DEFAULT_CHARSET[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[35m/[0m[39m* closeOnError = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m false,[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[35m/[0m[39m* ignoreLocalFileHeader = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m false,[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[35m/[0m[39m* allowRemoteComments = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m false[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     @Deprecated[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     public [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mSeekableByteChannel channel,[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    String channelDescription,[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    String encoding,[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    boolean useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    boolean ignoreLocalFileHeader[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mthis[0m[1;39m([0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             channel,[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             channelDescription,[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mCharsets.toCharset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mencoding, Builder.DEFAULT_CHARSET[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[35m/[0m[39m* closeOnError = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m false,[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             ignoreLocalFileHeader,[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[35m/[0m[39m* allowRemoteComments = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m false[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Private convenience converting String→Charset:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mSeekableByteChannel channel,[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     String channelDescription,[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     String encoding,[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     boolean useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     boolean closeOnError,[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     boolean ignoreLocalFileHeader[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mthis[0m[1;39m([0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             channel,[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             channelDescription,[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mCharsets.toCharset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mencoding, Builder.DEFAULT_CHARSET[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             closeOnError,[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             ignoreLocalFileHeader,[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[35m/[0m[39m* allowRemoteComments = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m false[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. The existing private constructor that accepted a `Charset` and six parameters[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis replaced by the new seven-parameter one shown above. Remove or collapse any [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mother private overloads so there is exactly one implementation.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Wire the flag through the builder API:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `ZipFile.Builder`, add:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private boolean allowRemoteComments = false;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      * Controls whether ZIP file comments beginning with [0m[32m"http"[0m[35m/[0m[32m"https"[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      * are fetched over the network.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     public Builder [0m[1;35msetAllowRemoteComments[0m[1;39m([0m[39mboolean allowRemoteComments[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         this.allowRemoteComments = allowRemoteComments;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return this;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `[0m[1;35mBuilder.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, change the constructor call:[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```diff[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - return new [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mactualChannel,[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     -                    actualDescription,[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     -                    [0m[1;35mgetCharset[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     -                    useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     -                    closeOnError,[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     -                    ignoreLocalFileHeader[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     + return new [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mactualChannel,[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     +                    actualDescription,[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     +                    [0m[1;35mgetCharset[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     +                    useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     +                    closeOnError,[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     +                    ignoreLocalFileHeader,[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     +                    allowRemoteComments[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Safeguard the SSRF-prone logic in `readCentralDirectoryEntry` by adding the new [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mguard:[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```diff[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   String commentString = [0m[1;35mentryEncoding.decode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcomment[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcommentString.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"http"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;35mcommentString.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"https"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   + if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mallowRemoteComments[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +     && [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcommentString.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"http"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mcommentString.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"https"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream is = new [0m[1;35mURL[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcommentString[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.openStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m fetch and override commentString[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mIOException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m swallow[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;35mze.setComment[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcommentString[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Verify there is no longer any constructor signature collision—every [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpublic/deprecated overload remains exactly as before, and only the private [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimplementation has gained the extra boolean. All delegates now match the unique [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mseven-parameter signature, so the compiler errors about duplicate signatures and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtype mismatches will be resolved.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Rebuild and run existing unit tests and the fuzz harness unchanged. The default [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbehavior [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`allowRemoteComments == false`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m continues to swallow any “http…” comments[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout network I/O, preserving backwards compatibility. Consumers who explicitly [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcall `[0m[1;35mBuilder.setAllowRemoteComments[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` can opt in to the new feature.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This approach cleanly injects the new SSRF‐mitigation flag without altering the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpublic API signatures or removing any existing deprecated constructors—avoiding [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mduplicate overloads.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- By centralizing logic in one private constructor, we eliminate charset‐vs‐string [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmismatches and ensure consistent flag handling.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Default behavior is unaffected, so no existing tests or harness code break.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The flag propagates only through `Builder`, which is the recommended modern API. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDeprecated constructors still work identically.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Potential side effects are minimal; network fetching only occurs when [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`allowRemoteComments` is true.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39morg.apache.commons.compress.archivers.zip.ZipFile.<init>[0m[1;39m([0m[39mZipFile.jav[0m[1;92ma:876[0m[1;39m)[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[39mat [0m[1;35mCompressZipFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCompressZipFuzzer.jav[0m[1;92ma:30[0m[1;39m)[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDEDUP_TOKEN: b38823cc610751ee[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== libFuzzer crashing input ==[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA Jazzer fuzzing run flagged a Server-Side Request Forgery [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSSRF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ZipFile.readCentralDirectoryEntry`, where ZIP file comments starting with “http” [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor “https” are fetched via `new [0m[1;35mURL[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.openStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. The patch attempt [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintroduced a new `allowRemoteComments` flag, updated the `Builder` API and all [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ZipFile` constructors to carry that flag, and wrapped the remote-fetch logic in an[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mallowRemoteComments[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` guard. After applying the patch, the build fails with [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtwo errors:  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Duplicate use of `@Deprecated` on the same method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mJava annotations are not [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrepeatable[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Numerous constructor calls no longer match any `ZipFile` constructor signature [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mmismatched parameter lists, incorrect use of `String` vs. `Charset`, missing [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mflag[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Jazzer reported a `FuzzerSecurityIssueMedium: Server Side Request Forgery [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mSSRF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, noting an attempted connection to `jazze.com:[0m[1;36m80[0m[39m`.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The SSRF originates in `ZipFile.readCentralDirectoryEntry`, which reads the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcentral directory comment into a `String` and, if it begins with “http” or “https”,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mopens a connection to that URL without restriction.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Stack trace highlights:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `ServerSideRequestForgery.checkSsrfSocket` → `Socket.connect`[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `HttpURLConnection.connect` → `URL.openStream`[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Called from [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`org.apache.commons.compress.archivers.zip.ZipFile.readCentralDirectoryEntry`[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **New Field & Builder Setter**  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added `private final boolean allowRemoteComments` to `ZipFile`.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Extended `Builder` with `[0m[1;35msetAllowRemoteComments[0m[1;39m([0m[39mboolean[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and defaulted the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnew flag to `false`.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Constructor Changes**  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Updated every deprecated and Builder-driven constructor overload to accept the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextra `allowRemoteComments` parameter, passing `false` by default for existing [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentry points.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Consolidated into a primary constructor:[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       SeekableByteChannel channel,[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       String description,[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       Charset encoding,[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       boolean useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       boolean closeOnError,[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       boolean ignoreLocalFileHeader,[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       boolean allowRemoteComments[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Conditional Fetch**  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Wrapped the URL fetch in:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mallowRemoteComments && [0m[1;35mcommentString.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"http"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[33m...[0m[39m [0m[1;35mopenStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Resulting Compilation Errors**  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Error [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: “java.lang.Deprecated is not a repeatable annotation type” at two [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethods where `@Deprecated` was inadvertently applied twice.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Error [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: “no suitable constructor found for [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mSeekableByteChannel, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mString, String, boolean, boolean, boolean[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m”  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Dozens of calls to `new [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` now pass a `String` for encoding and [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mone fewer or mismatched boolean flags than any declared constructor.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas for Further Investigation[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Constructor Consistency**  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Review all `ZipFile` constructor overloads and calls to ensure parameter lists [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malign:  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Decide between `String encoding` vs. `Charset encoding` in signatures.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Ensure every call site [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdeprecated overloads, Builder, internal forwarding[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpasses the correct number and types of arguments, including the new [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`allowRemoteComments` flag.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Annotation Usage**  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Remove duplicate `@Deprecated` annotations or consolidate into single [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurrences.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Builder API**  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Confirm `[0m[1;35mBuilder.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` invokes the correct constructor signature and propagates [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`allowRemoteComments`.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Remote-fetch Logic**  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Validate that the `allowRemoteComments` flag is consistently applied wherever [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomments are parsed, and review any other code paths that might trigger network [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalls based on untrusted data.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn SSRF [0m[1;39m([0m[39mServer Side Request Forgery[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m issue was detected by Jazzer while fuzzing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe Apache Commons Compress `ZipFile` class. The crash indicates that untrusted [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata led to an HTTP connection attempt [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`jazze.com:[0m[1;36m80[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m during ZIP processing.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA patch attempt modified all of the deprecated `ZipFile` constructors so they [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdelegate to a presumed new “master” constructor that takes a `SeekableByteChannel`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma description, a `Charset`, and four boolean flags [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`useUnicodeExtraFields`, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`closeOnError`, `ignoreLocalFileHeader`, `allowRemoteComments`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. After applying the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch, the build failed with repeated “no suitable constructor found” errors, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbecause no constructor with seven arguments matching that signature exists in the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclass.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Jazzer reported a `FuzzerSecurityIssueMedium: Server Side Request Forgery [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSSRF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mduring ZIP file parsing.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack trace shows an HTTP connection in [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`org.apache.commons.compress.archivers.zip.ZipFile.readCentralDirectoryEntry`, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtriggered by `URL.openStream`.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This indicates that ZIP processing code can make network requests based on [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muntrusted input, potentially exfiltrating data or exposing internal services.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mImportant Observations[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The vulnerable call path begins in Apache Commons Compress’s `ZipFile` [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructors and ZIP parsing logic.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All overloads of `new [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` ultimately open a stream to read the central [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdirectory, and that logic does not guard against remote URLs.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer harness used `CompressZipFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput` to feed arbitrary [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes into a `ZipFile` constructor.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The patch replaces each deprecated constructor overload, e.g.:[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Original:[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    public [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile file[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mthis[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfile, DEFAULT_CHARSET_NAME[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Patched:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    public [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile file[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mthis[0m[1;39m([0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mnewReadByteChannel[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mfile.toPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mfile.getAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mCharsets.toCharset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mDEFAULT_CHARSET_NAME, Builder.DEFAULT_CHARSET[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[35m/[0m[39m* useUnicodeExtraFields = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m true,[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[35m/[0m[39m* closeOnError = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m true,[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[35m/[0m[39m* ignoreLocalFileHeader = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m false,[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[35m/[0m[39m* allowRemoteComments = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m false[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Similar changes were applied to all other constructors [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwith `File`, `Path`, and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`SeekableByteChannel` parameters[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, uniformly passing seven arguments.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The intent appears to be consolidating constructor logic into a single internal [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructor that handles all configuration flags.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Result[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Compilation errors occur at each patched constructor call site, for example:[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  no suitable constructor found for  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mSeekableByteChannel,[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            String,[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            java.nio.charset.Charset,[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            boolean, boolean, boolean, boolean[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The existing class defines no constructor that accepts all seven parameters. The [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclosest existing constructor takes six arguments:[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mSeekableByteChannel channel,[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            String channelDescription,[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            Charset encoding,[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            boolean useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            boolean closeOnError,[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            boolean ignoreLocalFileHeader[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Because the patched calls pass an extra `allowRemoteComments` boolean, none of [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe constructors match, leading to “no suitable constructor” errors.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The set of constructors declared in `ZipFile.java`: verify the intended “master” [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructor signature and update all callers to match it.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The private/internal [0m[1;35mconstructor[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in `ZipFile` that actually implement file [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreading. Confirm whether an `allowRemoteComments` parameter exists or should be [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madded.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The `Builder` class for ZIP files: it may already centralize constructor logic [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand should be aligned with these overload changes.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The `newReadByteChannel` method import and definition: ensure it returns a [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`SeekableByteChannel` and that it is used consistently across all overloads.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The central-directory reading logic in `readCentralDirectoryEntry`: trace how [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mURIs or URLs are constructed and identify why `URL.openStream` is invoked.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzz harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`CompressZipFuzzer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to confirm it only feeds local ZIP bytes [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand cannot trigger remote I/O on its own.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo root cause or solution is proposed here; this report is intended to document the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39missue, the attempted patch, and the mismatches that caused the build failures.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/main/java/org/apache/commons/compress/archivers/zip/ZipFile.jav[0m[1;92ma:1550[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1556[0m      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1550[0m[39m:        String commentString = [0m[1;35mentryEncoding.decode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcomment[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1551[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcommentString.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"http"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1552[0m[39m:            try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream is = new [0m[1;35mURL[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcommentString[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.openStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1553[0m[39m:                ByteArrayOutputStream bos = new [0m[1;35mByteArrayOutputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mStandardCharsets.UTF_8[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1556[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mIOException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Introduce an allowRemoteComments flag in ZipFile and make it part of the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m“master” constructor:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Add a private final boolean allowRemoteComments field to the class.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Change the existing private constructor signature on lines ~[0m[1;36m896[0m[39m from six [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparameters to seven:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        private [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mSeekableByteChannel channel,[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        String channelDescription,[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        Charset encoding,[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        boolean useUnicodeExtraFields,[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        boolean closeOnError,[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        boolean ignoreLocalFileHeader,[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        boolean allowRemoteComments[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. In that constructor, assign this.allowRemoteComments = allowRemoteComments [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mearly, before any directory-reading logic.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Update all call sites [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdeprecated public constructors and Builder#[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. For each deprecated constructor, retain your previous patch to delegate into [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe new seven-parameter constructor, passing [0m[33mallowRemoteComments[0m[39m=[0m[35mfalse[0m[39m.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In Builder#[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mat around line [0m[1;36m168[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, change[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        return new [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mactualChannel, actualDescription, [0m[1;35mgetCharset[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                           useUnicodeExtraFields, closeOnError, [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mignoreLocalFileHeader[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      to[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        return new [0m[1;35mZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mactualChannel, actualDescription, [0m[1;35mgetCharset[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                           useUnicodeExtraFields, closeOnError, [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mignoreLocalFileHeader,[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                           [0m[35m/[0m[39m* allowRemoteComments = *[0m[35m/[0m[39m false[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Guard against SSRF in readCentralDirectoryEntry:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Locate the URL.openStream block [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m1552[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Change the condition:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcommentString.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"http"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;35mcommentString.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"https"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            && allowRemoteComments[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m existing remote-fetch logic[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      Thus, when allowRemoteComments is false [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe default[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, any “http…” comments [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mare treated as literal strings and no network calls occur.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preserve existing functionality:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Default behavior [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdeprecated constructors and [0m[1;35mBuilder.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m still disallow [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremote comment fetching.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – No changes to harness, utility methods, tests, or external libraries.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – All existing six-parameter calls have been updated to match the new [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mseven-parameter signature.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Document the change:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Update javadoc on Builder to mention the new allowRemoteComments option, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdefaulting to false.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Optionally provide a new [0m[1;35mBuilder.allowRemoteComments[0m[1;39m([0m[39mboolean[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method for [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madvanced users.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– By extending the master constructor instead of creating ad-hoc overloads, we [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munify all delegation paths and eliminate the “no suitable constructor” errors.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Guarding the URL.openStream call behind an explicit flag prevents untrusted data [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom triggering SSRF, satisfying the security requirement.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Defaulting allowRemoteComments to false preserves backward compatibility and [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting test behavior.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– No harness or test code is modified, so existing coverage and fuzzing logic [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremain intact.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
